{"tid":1654814,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［強制歸邊］杯葛狗務處","createTime":"2019-10-14T18:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T09:39:27.000Z","uid":246671,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7d88d5263f9de70bf2a8dbc1758f56779f0ea030","tid":1654814,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T18:29:16.000Z","msg":"1，善用已有資料<br />\n好多謝制作黃藍店名單app既手足，辛苦你地既用心，但我想講就咁得個名單係無用既，因為香港人既本質就係一班懶鳩<br />\n<br />\n就住呢個情況，小弟有少少建議，唔知有無可能用google map功能，當打開個app既時候，會<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自動alert</span></span>附近方圓廿米既藍店？其實我地唔需要好刻意去支持黄店，當藍店生意少左黃店生意自然會多<br />\n<br />\n2，主動杯葛主要目標<br />\n以下係警務處過往半年批出既供應商合約，希望大家拒絕甚至杯葛呢啲商家，目的係斷佢地軍需，等牠們屎都無得食<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qytPkQd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqytPkQd.jpg&h=58c2f3db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Rif0Qe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Rif0Qe.jpg&h=8b566f0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3，無限主動出擊<br />\n係作任何消費既時候，主動詢問收銀有無親屬係黑警，佢答有即時取消消費，目標係要所有店舖強制歸邊，否認有員工為黑警家屬<br />\n<br />\n唔敢上前線既各位，請係能力許可下盡量支持，多謝"},{"pid":"c212d8dfee5229bd2acc0b339a75fe912b0b44b8","tid":1654814,"uid":56665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T18:52:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b54ba5523fda139bf6d64cf6b0820a0cbd9ea6e","tid":1654814,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T19:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7MNgLMr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7MNgLMr.png&h=f90ad1a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iNKGcrs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiNKGcrs.png&h=351b8c75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d75fe4d52bb48529d9acd5873c32bd5c28158807","tid":1654814,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:26:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37263a3e4fabb1b